727593f-a.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 37th Street
727593f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, east from 37th to 38th
Streets. The gasoline station in the foreground occupies a
small triangular plot, and the low buildings across it are
on 37th Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  September 5, 1940
NO REPRODUCTIONS
